track.name: Bad to the Bone
comments: I fell in love with song the first time I heard it!
His shows are still b-b-b-bad to the bone!  Don't miss him if he's in your town!
The ol' MTV video circa 1982 of George shooting pool against Bo Diddley was a classic! Willie Mosconi bets heavy on Bo to win and well.. you know the rest.
"I NEED YOUR CLOTHES, YOUR BOOTS AND YOUR MOTORCYCLE"!!
BAD TO THE BONE MY THEME SONG!!!HA!
b b b b b BAD...
will always remind of al bundy. it's like it was written about him.
reminds me of the terminator film. Great stuff
